        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Welcome-to-My-Blog"><a href="#Welcome-to-My-Blog" class="headerlink" title="Welcome to My Blog"></a>Welcome to My Blog</h1><p>@(Sample Introduction)[LCD|Android Studio]</p><pre><code>在之前三个月VS项目中，我在团队中主要负责软件部分。</code></pre><p>Learn <strong>Java</strong> and <strong>AS</strong> to write and generate APP.<br>In this project, the graphical interface was developed in <strong>Android Studio</strong>, using Java programming language.Its main function is to provide customers with a comprehensive game, allowing developers to check all aspects, including sensors, communications and servo motors.</p><p>The upper computer use a <a href="http://wiki.friendlyarm.com/wiki/index.php/Smart4418">friendly</a> provided LCD screen.这是LCD一些端口的示意图，如果还需要更详细的了解，可以去友善官方去查看。</p><img src="/2021/05/05/css/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.jpg" class="" title="LCD端口"><h2 id="Requirement-of-project"><a href="#Requirement-of-project" class="headerlink" title="Requirement of project"></a>Requirement of project</h2><ul><li><strong>Two language modes</strong> - English mode and Chinese mode.</li><li><strong>Two operation modes</strong> - User mode and administrator mode.</li><li><strong>Fully automatic</strong>  - The entire game is automated from start to finish.</li><li><strong>User identification</strong> - By swiping the card.</li><li><strong>Guide user operation</strong> - through appropriate voice and text prompts.<br>大概最基础的就这几点,语言切换，模式，自动化，身份识别，语音提示，智能，哦对了还有通信，通信会在下一个part里说。</li></ul><hr><img src="/2021/05/05/css/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.jpg" class="" title="流程图"><p>这是一个简单的操作流程图，看不懂也没关系(=^▽^=)后面我主要说最基本的GUI的设计。</p><h2 id="GUI"><a href="#GUI" class="headerlink" title="GUI"></a>GUI</h2><blockquote><p>先放一张自己做的GUI</p></blockquote><img src="/2021/05/05/css/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.jpg" class="" title="GUI界面"><p>###Set up new projects<br>File-&gt;New-&gt;New project 选择Empty Activity -&gt;Next -&gt;</p><img src="/2021/05/05/css/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.jpg" class=""><p>Finish</p><p>###Introduction to each section<br>目录结构：<br><a href="http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000002963895">http://segmentfault.com/a/1190000002963895</a></p><p>在res-&gt;values-&gt;themes-&gt;themes.xml中更改为</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>style name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"Theme.自己名称"</span> parent<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"Theme.MaterialComponents.DayNight.NoActionBar.Bridge"</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>去除按钮原有背景色<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="Layout"><a href="#Layout" class="headerlink" title="Layout"></a>Layout</h3><img src="/2021/05/05/css/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.jpg" class=""><p>Code只看代码，Split代码＋图示，Design只看图示</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">?</span>xml version<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"1.0"</span> encoding<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"utf-8"</span><span class="token operator">?</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">LinearLayout</span> xmlns<span class="token operator">:</span>android<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>排版类型，有三种，建立新的<span class="token class-name">Layout</span>应该是<span class="token class-name"><span class="token namespace">androidx<span class="token punctuation">.</span>constraintlayout<span class="token punctuation">.</span>widget<span class="token punctuation">.</span></span>ConstraintLayout</span>，在这种下你可以拖拽组件布置页面，还有<span class="token class-name">LinearLayout</span>和<span class="token class-name">RelativeLayout</span>，我习惯使用<span class="token class-name">LinearLayout</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>    xmlns<span class="token operator">:</span>app<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"</span>    xmlns<span class="token operator">:</span>tools<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"http://schemas.android.com/tools"</span>    android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"match_parent"</span>    android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"match_parent"</span>    android<span class="token operator">:</span>orientation<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"vertical"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token class-name">LinearLayout</span>必须设置，vertical垂直分布，horizontal水平分布<span class="token punctuation">}</span>    tools<span class="token operator">:</span>context<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">".MainActivity"</span>    android<span class="token operator">:</span>background<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@drawable/bk4"</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>背景设置<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>wrap_content和match_parent区别可以看这里<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_45842760/article/details/113403956">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_45842760/article/details/113403956</a></p><h4 id="Common-components"><a href="#Common-components" class="headerlink" title="Common components"></a>Common components</h4><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">TextView</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>不可改文本<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/main11"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>养成写id的习惯，在java文件里调用时用到<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"请选择语言:"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>显示的文本<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_gravity<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"center"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>居中<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>textStyle<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"bold"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>文本加粗<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>textSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"32sp"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>文本大小<span class="token punctuation">,</span>sp<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">ImageView</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>可加图片文本<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"40dp"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"40dp"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@drawable/flow"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>添加图片<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_marginLeft<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"8dp"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_marginTop<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"10dp"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">EditText</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>可更改文本<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/plytex1"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>hint<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"请输入密码"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>暗文，输入之前的底部文字<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textColorHint<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@color/white"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>暗文颜色<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textStyle<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"bold"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>inputType<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"textPassword"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>隐藏密码<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textColor<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"#ffc22a"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"26sp"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">Button</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>按钮<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/change1"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_marginLeft<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"286dp"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>整个组件离左侧的距离<span class="token punctuation">,</span>dp<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"开始游戏"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>textStyle<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"bold"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>textColor<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"#4f4f45"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>文本颜色<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>textSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"43sp"</span>        style<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"?android:attr/borderlessButtonStyle"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>可不添加，此功能为使其透明与背景相容<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">ImageButton</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>可加图片按钮<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/gongg"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"53dp"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"53dp"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>scaleType<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"centerInside"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>显示在中心<span class="token punctuation">}</span>             android<span class="token operator">:</span>src<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@drawable/home"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>添加图片<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>想了解scaleType用法可见<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/linglingchenchen/article/details/53840911">https://blog.csdn.net/linglingchenchen/article/details/53840911</a></p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">RadioGroup</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>单选按钮组<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/rg1"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">RadioButton</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/rb1"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"中文"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textStyle<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"bold"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>checked<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"true"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>一开始选中<span class="token punctuation">}</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"28sp"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">RadioButton</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/rb2"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"English"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textStyle<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"bold"</span>            android<span class="token operator">:</span>textSize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"28sp"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token class-name">RadioGroup</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">CheckBox</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>复选框<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/sport_cb"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>checked<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"true"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>一开始选中<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"运动"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">CheckBox</span>         android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/reading_cb"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>checked<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"true"</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>一开始选中<span class="token punctuation">}</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"看书"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span>    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token class-name">CheckBox</span>         android<span class="token operator">:</span>id<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"@+id/game_cb"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_width<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>layout_height<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"wrap_content"</span>        android<span class="token operator">:</span>text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"游戏"</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">&gt;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>上方只要有{}括起来的都为解释说明，需去掉。</p><h3 id="Component-invocation-in-Java"><a href="#Component-invocation-in-Java" class="headerlink" title="Component invocation in Java"></a>Component invocation in Java</h3><p>$$    最初Java文件，也就是你的MainActivity$$</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">package</span> <span class="token namespace">com<span class="token punctuation">.</span>example<span class="token punctuation">.</span>triangle</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token namespace">androidx<span class="token punctuation">.</span>appcompat<span class="token punctuation">.</span>app<span class="token punctuation">.</span></span><span class="token class-name">AppCompatActivity</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token namespace">android<span class="token punctuation">.</span>os<span class="token punctuation">.</span></span><span class="token class-name">Bundle</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">MainActivity</span> <span class="token keyword">extends</span> <span class="token class-name">AppCompatActivity</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token annotation punctuation">@Override</span>    <span class="token keyword">protected</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">onCreate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">Bundle</span> savedInstanceState<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">super</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">onCreate</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>savedInstanceState<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token function">setContentView</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token class-name">R</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>layout<span class="token punctuation">.</span>activity_MainActivity<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>$$    更改后Java文件$$</p><pre class="line-numbers language-java" data-language="java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token clas